pageContext.claim: “New Lott study estimates 11,350 absentee votes lost to Trump in Georgia. Another 289,000 "excess (fraudulent) votes" across GA, AZ, MI, NV, PA, and WI.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump touts a study by a controversial gun-rights analyst whose research has often been questioned. He is not an expert on elections. The study offers estimates and is not evidence that fraud took place.
